<!DOCTYPE html>


<html data-theme="light" lang="es">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8"/>
<meta content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" name="viewport"/>
<title>Slide 5 - Problema</title>
<link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/tailwindcss@2.2.19/dist/tailwind.min.css" rel="stylesheet"/>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" rel="preconnect"/>
<link crossorigin="" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" rel="preconnect"/>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700&amp;display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
<link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet"/>
<style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f3f4f6;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
        }
        .slide-container {
            width: 1024px;
            height: 768px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            position: relative;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .font-poppins {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
        }
        .text-corporate-blue {
            color: #114a90;
        }
        .bg-corporate-blue {
            background-color: #114a90;
        }
        .text-corporate-red {
            color: #C0504D;
        }
        .bg-corporate-red {
            background-color: #C0504D;
        }
        .border-corporate-red {
            border-color: #C0504D;
        }
        .border-corporate-blue {
            border-color: #114a90;
        }
        .bg-light-gray {
            background-color: #F9FAFB;
        }
        .problem-card {
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
        }
        .problem-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 8px 10px -6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="slide-container font-poppins">
<header class="w-full h-24 flex items-end justify-between px-12 pb-4 relative z-10" data-object="true" data-object-type="textbox" style="position: relative; width: 1024px; height: 96px;">
<div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-2 bg-corporate-red"></div>
<div class="flex flex-col">
<div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-1">
<span class="w-8 h-1 bg-corporate-red"></span>
<p class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-widest">El Problema</p>
</div>
<h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-corporate-blue">¿Te identificas con esto?</h2>
</div>
<div class="flex flex-col items-end">
<p class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-200">05</p>
</div>
</header>
<main class="flex-1 px-16 py-8 flex flex-col justify-center relative" data-object="true" data-object-type="textbox" style="position: relative; width: 1024px; height: 672px;">
<div class="absolute right-0 top-20 w-64 h-64 bg-gray-50 rounded-full -z-10 opacity-50"></div>
<div class="absolute left-10 bottom-10 w-32 h-32 bg-blue-50 rounded-full -z-10 opacity-50"></div>
<div class="mb-8 w-3/4">
<p class="text-xl text-gray-600 font-light leading-relaxed">
                    Muchos dueños de negocios locales enfrentan los mismos desafíos al intentar gestionar sus redes sociales. <span class="font-semibold text-corporate-red">No estás solo.</span>
</p>
</div>
<div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-8 h-full pb-8">
<div class="problem-card bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md flex items-center gap-6 relative overflow-hidden group">
<div class="absolute left-0 top-0 bottom-0 w-2 bg-gray-200 group-hover:bg-corporate-red transition-colors duration-300"></div>
<div class="w-16 h-16 flex-shrink-0 bg-red-50 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-corporate-red text-2xl group-hover:bg-corporate-red group-hover:text-white transition-all duration-300">
<i class="fa-solid fa-circle-question"></i>
</div>
<div>
<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-1 group-hover:text-corporate-blue transition-colors">Incertidumbre</h3>
<p class="text-lg text-gray-600">"No sé qué publicar"</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="problem-card bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md flex items-center gap-6 relative overflow-hidden group">
<div class="absolute left-0 top-0 bottom-0 w-2 bg-gray-200 group-hover:bg-corporate-red transition-colors duration-300"></div>
<div class="w-16 h-16 flex-shrink-0 bg-red-50 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-corporate-red text-2xl group-hover:bg-corporate-red group-hover:text-white transition-all duration-300">
<i class="fa-solid fa-hourglass-half"></i>
</div>
<div>
<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-1 group-hover:text-corporate-blue transition-colors">Ineficiencia</h3>
<p class="text-lg text-gray-600">"Me lleva horas crear contenido"</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="problem-card bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md flex items-center gap-6 relative overflow-hidden group">
<div class="absolute left-0 top-0 bottom-0 w-2 bg-gray-200 group-hover:bg-corporate-red transition-colors duration-300"></div>
<div class="w-16 h-16 flex-shrink-0 bg-red-50 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-corporate-red text-2xl group-hover:bg-corporate-red group-hover:text-white transition-all duration-300">
<i class="fa-solid fa-map-location-dot"></i>
</div>
<div>
<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-1 group-hover:text-corporate-blue transition-colors">Falta de Rumbo</h3>
<p class="text-lg text-gray-600">"Publico sin estrategia"</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="problem-card bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md flex items-center gap-6 relative overflow-hidden group">
<div class="absolute left-0 top-0 bottom-0 w-2 bg-gray-200 group-hover:bg-corporate-red transition-colors duration-300"></div>
<div class="w-16 h-16 flex-shrink-0 bg-red-50 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-corporate-red text-2xl group-hover:bg-corporate-red group-hover:text-white transition-all duration-300">
<i class="fa-solid fa-heart-crack"></i>
</div>
<div>
<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-1 group-hover:text-corporate-blue transition-colors">Bajo Impacto</h3>
<p class="text-lg text-gray-600">"Mis posts no generan engagement"</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</main>
</div>

    <div style="position: fixed; bottom: 20px; right: 20px; z-index: 9999; display: flex; gap: 10px; font-family: sans-serif; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">
        <a href="/slide-5" style="padding: 10px 15px; background: #114a90; color: #fff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; opacity: 1; pointer-events: auto">Anterior</a>
        <span style="padding: 10px 15px; background: #fff; color: #333; border-radius: 5px; border: 1px solid #ccc;">6 / 26</span>
        <a href="/slide-7" style="padding: 10px 15px; background: #114a90; color: #fff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; opacity: 1; pointer-events: auto">Siguiente</a>
    </div>
    
</body>
</html>


